[I] A modern X11 server written from scratch in Rust

[T] A modern X11 server written from scratch in Rust.

[U] https://github.com/joske/yserver

[A] joske
[M] The T2 Project <t2@t2-project.org>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS NO-LTO

[L] MIT
[V] 1.0.0

[D] e02f68f33eb8684c8da60bd8aa3504edef949768f688b06e5b5f91a5 yserver-1.0.0.tar.gz https://github.com/joske/yserver/archive/v1.0.0/

runjust=0 cargoinstopt=

var_append GCC_WRAPPER_APPEND ' ' -L$root$(pkgprefix libdir xkbcommon)
atstage cross && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/${arch_target}/*/yserver $root$bindir/"
atstage native && hook_add postmake 5 "install target/*/yserver $root$bindir/"
